    <div id="header">
      <div id="logo">
        <h1><a href="/"><b>MarkdownSha.re</b></a></h1>
        <h4>Simple sharing of markdown text</h4>
      </div>
      <div id="links">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/" title="Home">Home</a></li>
          <li><a href="/create/" title="Create">Create</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>&nbsp;</p>
    <blockquote>
      <h1>Welcome to <tt>Markdownsha.re</tt></h1>
      <blockquote>
        <p>This site allows you to easily paste some Markdown-formatted text, and share it with the world.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>No fees.</li>
          <li>No account.</li>
          <li>No restrictions.</li>
        </ul>
        <p><a href="/create">Share your markdown</a>.</p>
      </blockquote>

      <h2>API</h2>
      <blockquote>
        <p>Rather than using the website you can submit text by POSTing your data to the <a href="/create">creation end-point</a>:</p>
<pre>
$ curl -H "Accept: application/json" -X POST --data "text=text+goes+here" http://markdownsha.re/create/
</pre>
<p>Or from the contents of a file:</p>
<pre>
$ curl -H "Accept: application/json" -X POST -F "text=&lt;/path/to/text.md" http://markdownsha.re/create/

</pre>
      </blockquote>
    </blockquote>
    <p></p>
